  <div class="stepdescription"><div class="images-holder" data-entry-url="/id/Easy-Bean-Burgers/"><a name="images"></a><div class="spot-holder"><div id="spot370296" class="image-spot"><div class='sizer'><a data-imageid='FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0' href='/image/FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0' id='infolink_spot370296' class='withBG image-spot-info' style='display:none;'>i</a><div id='tooltip_spot370296' class='withBG image-spot-tooltip' style='display:none;'>Image Information</div><img id='img_spot370296' class='photo id_FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0' src='/image/FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0/Easy-Bean-Burgers.jpg' GALLERYIMG='NO' alt='Easy Bean Burgers' /></div></div>
</div><div id="spot370296_spots" class="image-show-container"><a id="spot370296_spots_prev_row" href="#" class="prev-row">&laquo;</a><div class="spotThumbs image-show clearfix"><ul><li><a class="spot-thumb" href="/files/deriv/FF9/CPKD/GQZJMGA0/FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0.MEDIUM.jpg" data-fileurl="/files/orig/FF9/CPKD/GQZJMGA0/FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0.jpg" id="imgThumb_spot370296_FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0"><img id="id_FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0" src="http://img.instructables.com/files/deriv/FF9/CPKD/GQZJMGA0/FF9CPKDGQZJMGA0.SQUARE.jpg" alt="IMG_2327.JPG" /></a></li><li><a class="spot-thumb" href="/files/deriv/F1V/V71U/GQZJMTQK/F1VV71UGQZJMTQK.MEDIUM.jpg" data-fileurl="/files/orig/F1V/V71U/GQZJMTQK/F1VV71UGQZJMTQK.jpg" id="imgThumb_spot370296_F1VV71UGQZJMTQK"><img id="id_F1VV71UGQZJMTQK" src="http://img.instructables.com/files/deriv/F1V/V71U/GQZJMTQK/F1VV71UGQZJMTQK.SQUARE.jpg" alt="IMG_2326.JPG" /></a></li><li><a class="spot-thumb" href="/files/deriv/F69/ORPD/GQZJMTQE/F69ORPDGQZJMTQE.MEDIUM.jpg" data-fileurl="/files/orig/F69/ORPD/GQZJMTQE/F69ORPDGQZJMTQE.jpg" id="imgThumb_spot370296_F69ORPDGQZJMTQE"><img id="id_F69ORPDGQZJMTQE" src="http://img.instructables.com/files/deriv/F69/ORPD/GQZJMTQE/F69ORPDGQZJMTQE.SQUARE.jpg" alt="IMG_2325.JPG" /></a></li><li><a class="spot-thumb" href="/files/deriv/FOE/HFCP/GQZJMGD1/FOEHFCPGQZJMGD1.MEDIUM.jpg" data-fileurl="/files/orig/FOE/HFCP/GQZJMGD1/FOEHFCPGQZJMGD1.jpg" id="imgThumb_spot370296_FOEHFCPGQZJMGD1"><img id="id_FOEHFCPGQZJMGD1" src="http://img.instructables.com/files/deriv/FOE/HFCP/GQZJMGD1/FOEHFCPGQZJMGD1.SQUARE.jpg" alt="IMG_2348.JPG" /></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="txt">
              
                       <div class="summary">
              
            <br />
These bean burgers are super easy and very quick to make - not to mention you can add in so many things to suit your tastes! This is just a base recipe, so go wild. :D<br />
<br />
These take about 30-45 minutes to make, and have a very short ingredient list. One can of beans can make four burgers!<br />

          
                   </div>
          
        </div><div id="files"><a name="files"></a></div>
        
        
                 <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="adwrapper">
                 <tr>
