        <div class="remove-ads"><img src="/static/img/dialog-close.png" align="absmiddle" class="ex" alt="Remove these ads" />Remove these ads by
          <a href="/account/gopro?sourcea=removeads&nxtPgName=Easy+Bean+Burgers&nxtPg=/id/Easy-Bean-Burgers/"><strong>Signing Up</strong></a></div><a name="step1">&nbsp;</a><h2><span class="stepLabel">Step 1</span><span class="stepTitle">Ingredients + hardware!</span></h2><div class="images-holder" data-entry-url="/id/Easy-Bean-Burgers/step1/Ingredients-hardware/"><a name="images"></a><div class="spot-holder"><div id="spot370297" class="image-spot"><div class='sizer'><a data-imageid='F33E02AGQZJMG4P' href='/image/F33E02AGQZJMG4P' id='infolink_spot370297' class='withBG image-spot-info' style='display:none;'>i</a><div id='tooltip_spot370297' class='withBG image-spot-tooltip' style='display:none;'>Image Information</div><img id='img_spot370297' class='photo id_F33E02AGQZJMG4P' src='/image/F33E02AGQZJMG4P/Ingredients-hardware.jpg' GALLERYIMG='NO' alt='Ingredients + hardware!' /></div></div>
</div></div><div class="txt"><div class="instructions"><br />
Ingredients:
<ul>
	<li>
		1 14 oz. can OR 2 cups beans of your choice (I'm using chickpeas &amp; black beans)</li>
	<li>
		1 medium onion, cut into large chunks</li>
	<li>
		1/2 cup rolled oats (not instant)</li>
	<li>
		1 tbsp spice of your choice (I'm using chili powder in the black beans, cumin in the chickpeas)</li>
	<li>
		salt and pepper to taste</li>
	<li>
		1 egg</li>
	<li>
		oil for cooking (olive or canola)</li>
</ul>
Hardware:
<ul>
	<li>
		large pan for frying</li>
	<li>
		food processor</li>
	<li>
		spatulas, forks, etc.</li>
	<li>
		cutting boards</li>
</ul>
</div></div><div id="files"><a name="files"></a></div></div><table class="nextprev"><tr><td><a id="prevstepbutton" class="big-button disabled" href="#" onclick="return false;">&laquo; Previous Step</a></td><td width="100%" class="upsell"><span id="pdf_steps"><a href="#" class="gray-btn">Download PDF</a></span><script type="text/javascript">
